HEADWORD: Water tree
<hw>Wa"ter tree`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A climbing
shrub (<spn>Tetracera alnifolia</spn> syn. <spn>Tetracera
potatoria</spn>) of <geog>Western Africa</geog>, which pours out a
watery sap from the freshly cut stems.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water trefoil</ent>⟦br⟧
